Remarks
-------
implementing the memory has always the same pattern, selecting the memory
address by using some Dmux-chip and than, attachments one-level-lower chips,
after that selecting the output using som mux-chip.  

  DMux...(....);
  LOWMEMORYCHIP(.....);
  LOWMEMORYCHIP(.....);
  LOWMEMORYCHIP(.....);
  LOWMEMORYCHIP(.....);
  LOWMEMORYCHIP(.....);
  LOWMEMORYCHIP(.....);
  LOWMEMORYCHIP(.....);
  LOWMEMORYCHIP(.....);
  Mux...(....);
